Full Description: Flickup is a mobile app that connects nearby users to take a picture and send instantly, without ever handing over your phone. Group shots, individual photo capturing a significant location, and even candid’s can all be taken with a quick request. They eliminate the need to debate over whom to approach for a photo. With custom functionality, their users never have to hand their phone to a stranger again. Along with this, each user gets a star rating based upon how good the photos they’ve taken come out, eliminating this risk of having a bad photo taken.
